# Trivy Ignore File
# Temporary exemptions for known CVEs
# Format: CVE-ID
# Each entry MUST include:
#   - Reason for exemption
#   - Planned fix date
#   - Risk assessment

# Example (DO NOT USE IN PRODUCTION):
# CVE-2021-44228
#   Reason: Log4j vulnerability in dev dependencies only
#   Planned Fix: 2026-06-15
#   Risk: Not used in production, dev-only dependency

# Current exemptions:
# (No exemptions currently)

# IMPORTANT:
# - Review this file monthly
# - Remove exemptions as soon as patches are available
# - Document risk mitigation measures for each exemption
# - Maximum exemption period: 90 days